Subject: scsi: libcxgbi: Fix a use after free in cxgbi_conn_xmit_pdu()
Git-commit: 38660389a7697ae6dd56edfac5d87754374f217a
Patch-mainline: v5.9-rc5
References: bsc#1176695 jsc#sle-15116

We accidentally move this logging printk after the free, but that leads to
a use after free.

